* Equilibrated POPC bilayer: 256 POPC and 6596 TIP3 
* System Size: 93.5008 X 93.5008 X 58.73732
*

! Read topology
open read card unit 10 name top_all27_prot_lipid.rtf
read  rtf card unit 10
close unit 10

! Read parameters
open read card unit 10 name par_all27_prot_lipid_new.prm  
read para card unit 10
close unit 10

! Read PSF
open read card unit 10 name popc_n256.psf
read psf  card unit 10 

! Read Coordinate
open read card unit 10 name popc_n256.crd
read coor card unit 10 


!
! PBC & Energy setup
!

calc A = sqrt( 256 / 2.0 * 68.3 ) ! 68.3 A**2 / POPC at 303 K
calc B = @A
calc C = 58.73732

open read unit 10 card name crystal_image.str
CRYSTAL DEFINE TETRAGONAL @A @B @C 90.0 90.0 90.0
CRYSTAL READ UNIT 10 CARD

!Image centering by residue
IMAGE BYRESID XCEN 0.0 YCEN 0.0 ZCEN 0.0 

! Nonbonded Options

calc FFTx = 108
calc FFTy = 108
calc FFTz = 72

nbonds atom vatom vfswitch bycb -
       ctonnb 10.0 ctofnb 12.0 cutnb 16.0 cutim 16.0 -
       inbfrq -1 imgfrq -1 wmin 1.0 cdie eps 1.0 -
         ewald pmew fftx @fftx ffty @ffty fftz @fftz  kappa .34 spline order 6


energy

stop
